page.title: 04HEDGE STUDY, LITTLE URSWICK.
page.content: Huntide Lane,11th June 1985. Complete list of plants found. PLANTS: Dandelion,Cow Parsley,Hedge Bedstraw,Red Campion,Pink Campion, Lords and Ladies,Stinging Nettles, Dead Nettles,Buttercups,Bracken, Bindweed,Moss,Spurge,Wild Garlic, Clover,Bugle,Greater Celandine, Daisy,Sorrel,Germander Speedwell, Hedge Parsley,Ground Ivy,Spear Thistle,Shining Cranesbill,Cut Leaved Cranesbill,Yarrow. TREES AND SHRUBS. Sycamore,Hawthorn,Wych Elm,Ash,Hazel, Wild Rose,Oak,Blackberry,Elderberry. GRASSES: Tor Grass,Sea Couch Grass,Crested HairGrass,Tufted Hair Grass,Giant FescueGrass,Timothy Grass,Rye Grass, Fox Tail Grass,Cock's Foot Grass, Meadow Barley.
